Availability Comments (en):
The stock of fertilizers available is insufficient to cover the needs of the season, in particular for food crops (rice and vegetables);                                                               
The following imports are planned:
30,400 tonnes of urea;
21,600 tonnes of NPK 15 15 15;
1,200 tonnes of fertilizer for cotton.

